The paper discusses the use of provenance analysis for online multimedia, specifically focusing on digital image forensics and cultural analytics. This suggests that the paper is likely to fall under the categories of Multimedia (cs.MM), Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV), Cryptography and Security (cs.CR), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), and Machine Learning (cs.DL).
